product_name: Nike Cortez (Women's) Sneakers in Baroque Brown/Sail/Khaki
description: The Nike Cortez (Women's) Sneakers in Baroque Brown/Sail/Khaki revamps the classic Cortez runner design with a contemporary colorway of Baroque Brown, Sail, and khaki. Maintaining its 1972 retro appeal, the Baroque Brown (Women's) Nike Cortez boasts a soft foam midsole in Sail with a khaki-colored wedge beneath the heel. The jagged design on the rubber outsole represents another heritage detail and increases traction. Reinventing the design for contemporary audiences, the sneaker offers a wider toebox than the original for lasting comfort. Baroque Brown covers the shiny textile upper and the suede details on the toebox overlay, the heel counter, and the eyelets. On the other hand, splashes of Sail on the Swoosh logos, the laces, the tongue, the heel tab, and the rubber outsole provide subtle color-blocking and a premium feel. Our experts like the way khaki balances the color combination and appears on the branding details. The women’s size Nike Cortez (Women's) Sneakers in Baroque Brown/Sail/Khaki was released on April 2, 2024, and sold for $90.
